1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:13,000
"Double Helix"

2
00:01:13,700 --> 00:01:17,700
(Episode 9: Never Disliked, Always Liked)

3
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:20,599
About the job...

4
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,959
I'd like to talk to you
about it one more time.

5
00:01:23,159 --> 00:01:24,159
Of course,

6
00:01:24,439 --> 00:01:26,000
if you don't want to see me again,

7
00:01:26,959 --> 00:01:27,959
then forget it.

8
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,800
Sit wherever you like.

9
00:02:46,639 --> 00:02:47,839
Have something to drink first.

10
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,400
Lu Feng.

11
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,520
I...

12
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,599
I came here to explain things to you.

13
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:15,039
I wasn't using Ke Lo.

14
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:18,680
I actually just met Ke Lo.

15
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,840
He knew I was looking for a job,

16
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,879
so he brought me to your company.

17
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,680
When I came to see you,

18
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,599
I wanted to apologize.

19
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:45,759
I remember orange juice
used to be your favorite.

20
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:48,919
Don't you like it anymore?

21
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,680
No, that's not it.

22
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,080
I've always liked it.

23
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,760
You just said you wanted to apologize.

24
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,759
Apologize for what?

25
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,719
What have you done that
you need to apologize for?

26
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,279
Five years ago...

27
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,800
I'm sorry.

28
00:04:19,639 --> 00:04:22,839
My mind was a mess back then.

29
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:27,639
With what suddenly happened
to my brother and my mom...

30
00:04:28,319 --> 00:04:31,079
I just didn't know what to do.

31
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,959
Back then...

32
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,399
In my life,

33
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,799
I was only ever sure about Cheng Yichen.

34
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:44,200
If you want to break up, then fine.

35
00:04:47,079 --> 00:04:48,079
Lu Feng.

36
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,720
I heard...

37
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,600
you married Zhuo Lan.

38
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,639
Congratulations.

39
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,439
That's because...

40
00:05:00,639 --> 00:05:01,639
I also heard...

41
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,160
you two got divorced.

42
00:05:08,079 --> 00:05:10,160
The prized son-in-law
of the richest family.

43
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:11,879
Didn't that work out for you?

44
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:18,360
You're coming to me now...

45
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:20,439
is it because...

46
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:22,920
Zhuo Lan dumped you?

47
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:27,480
Or is it because you found out...

48
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:30,439
that I'm more powerful
than the Zhuo family,

49
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:32,160
so you dumped her?

50
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:41,600
What's wrong?

51
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,759
You look so pale.

52
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,720
Are you not feeling well?

53
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:49,680
I need to use the restroom.

54
00:05:58,079 --> 00:06:00,199
Did I say something to scare you?

55
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,040
You don't have to be afraid.

56
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,800
The past...

57
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,519
I've mostly forgotten about it.

58
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,319
Back then,

59
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,519
I really had nothing.

60
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:16,680
I certainly couldn't
compare to the Zhuo family.

61
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,120
So for you to change your mind...

62
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:22,720
it's not surprising.

63
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:24,480
But...

64
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,600
why didn't you just talk to me?

65
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:30,639
You made me run off to America,

66
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:33,120
give up everything,

67
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:36,199
and completely cut ties with the Lu family.

68
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,720
When I came back looking for you,

69
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,120
you were already married.

70
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,280
I couldn't find you no
matter how hard I looked.

71
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,959
What exactly do you want now?

72
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,439
First, you tell me.

73
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,280
Have you been waiting
for me all these years?

74
00:07:13,959 --> 00:07:15,120
Have you always loved me?

75
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:19,040
And now you want to rekindle our old flame?

76
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,199
You're burning up.

77
00:07:31,439 --> 00:07:32,600
Do you have a fever?

78
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:47,399
You're so manipulative.

79
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,200
Still carrying this piece of junk around.

80
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,399
Lu...

81
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,600
Lu Feng.

82
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:39,679
Lu Feng!

83
00:12:38,279 --> 00:12:39,279
Your house is huge!

84
00:12:39,279 --> 00:12:40,279
Lu...

85
00:12:41,120 --> 00:12:43,039
Mr. Lu, why is there someone in your house?

86
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,080
Don't mind him.

87
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,919
Mr. Lu, who is he?

88
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:55,799
Laugh.

89
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,559
Go on, laugh.

90
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:38,960
Lu Feng.

91
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,759
Let's talk.

92
00:13:40,879 --> 00:13:41,879
Talk about what?

93
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:44,840
About how you betrayed me?

94
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:48,119
It was because of my mom
and my brother back then.

95
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,120
I had no choice.

96
00:13:51,799 --> 00:13:53,320
Your mom and your brother?

97
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,159
What are they to me?

98
00:13:58,159 --> 00:14:00,080
Why should I have to consider them?

99
00:14:02,399 --> 00:14:03,879
So you tricked me into coming here...

100
00:14:05,440 --> 00:14:06,519
just to get revenge on me?

101
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:09,200
Revenge?

102
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,480
As if you're worthy.

103
00:14:15,279 --> 00:14:16,480
Then what is it you want?

104
00:14:41,879 --> 00:14:43,320
You're awful.

105
00:14:48,679 --> 00:14:49,720
Mr. Lu.

106
00:14:50,159 --> 00:14:51,279
Slow down.

107
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:54,720
Don't.

108
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,720
Mr. Lu.

109
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:01,960
Naughty.

110
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:04,759
Mr. Lu.

111
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,360
Don't.

112
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:19,000
Mr. Lu.

113
00:15:19,399 --> 00:15:20,399
Slow down.

114
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,200
Don't.

115
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,200
Naughty.

116
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:33,960
Mr. Lu.

117
00:16:40,919 --> 00:16:43,320
Mr. Lu, it's my first time at your place.

118
00:16:43,679 --> 00:16:45,000
I'm so happy.

119
00:17:00,159 --> 00:17:01,959
Mr. Lu, there's someone else here.

120
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,639
Why did you ask me to come over?

121
00:17:05,519 --> 00:17:07,199
You don't have to treat him like a person.

122
00:17:16,799 --> 00:17:18,279
You stepped on my foot.

123
00:17:18,559 --> 00:17:21,079
Mr. Lu, look at him.

124
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,600
He's not watching where he's going.

125
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:32,400
Apologize to him.

126
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,200
That's not necessary.

127
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,200
I said,

128
00:17:38,079 --> 00:17:39,079
apologize to him.

129
00:17:48,839 --> 00:17:49,839
I'm sorry.

130
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,440
Forget it, forget it.

131
00:17:55,319 --> 00:17:56,400
Was that fun?

132
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:48,799
Suddenly, it feels like in this world,

133
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:52,079
it's just the two of us left.

134
00:18:54,279 --> 00:18:55,359
Swear to me now.

135
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,039
Swear it.

136
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,560
That no matter what happens,

137
00:19:00,680 --> 00:19:02,160
you will never leave me again.

138
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:05,359
What if...

139
00:19:06,359 --> 00:19:07,839
you're the one who tells me to leave?

140
00:19:13,240 --> 00:19:14,279
You still can't leave.

141
00:19:16,759 --> 00:19:18,000
You're being so unreasonable.

142
00:19:19,559 --> 00:19:21,519
Yes or no?

143
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,680
Yes.

144
00:19:25,319 --> 00:19:27,119
As long as it's a request from you,

145
00:19:28,200 --> 00:19:29,480
no matter how unreasonable,

146
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:31,559
I'll accept it.

147
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:39,039
But if you leave me,

148
00:19:42,359 --> 00:19:44,480
I'll stop at nothing to find you

149
00:19:46,079 --> 00:19:47,240
to drag you back.

150
00:19:48,279 --> 00:19:49,440
I'll lock you up,

151
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:51,880
so you can never escape again.

152
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,680
Understand?

153
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,480
What does that matter?

154
00:20:02,680 --> 00:20:03,720
As long as...

155
00:20:04,279 --> 00:20:05,440
you love me.

156
00:20:17,319 --> 00:20:18,319
Lu Feng.

157
00:20:20,599 --> 00:20:21,599
Lu Feng.

158
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:34,720
Lu Feng.

159
00:20:35,119 --> 00:20:36,400
What were you dreaming about?

160
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:39,440
You were talking in your sleep.

161
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:42,440
What are you doing here?

162
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,119
This is my house.

163
00:20:49,279 --> 00:20:51,039
How long has it been
since you've had water?

164
00:20:51,799 --> 00:20:52,799
Drink.

165
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,400
You're not drinking?

166
00:21:00,319 --> 00:21:00,960
Suit yourself.

167
00:21:01,200 --> 00:21:01,599
Lu Feng.

168
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,680
Don't touch me.

169
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,440
What do you want from me?

170
00:21:13,839 --> 00:21:15,358
This feeling of being utterly helpless,

171
00:21:15,359 --> 00:21:16,720
where your pleas go unanswered...

172
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:20,440
seeing me be intimate
with other men every day...

173
00:21:22,359 --> 00:21:23,359
how does it feel?

174
00:21:28,519 --> 00:21:29,880
It feels terrible, doesn't it?

175
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:32,079
What right do you have to feel terrible?

176
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,480
Who are you to me?

177
00:21:35,359 --> 00:21:36,359
Mr. Zhuo.

178
00:21:42,799 --> 00:21:44,279
Looking at your face now,

179
00:21:45,599 --> 00:21:47,279
it makes me sick to my stomach.

180
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:49,880
Then why are you keeping me locked up here?

181
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,200
Let me go.

182
00:21:56,839 --> 00:21:57,839
You want to leave?

183
00:22:03,039 --> 00:22:03,799
In your dreams.

184
00:22:04,039 --> 00:22:05,640
This is false imprisonment.

185
00:22:09,920 --> 00:22:10,920
Then call the police.

186
00:22:13,599 --> 00:22:15,239
It's not like you haven't done it before.

187
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:18,640
Or...

188
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:21,200
you could kill me in my sleep.

189
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,480
Kill me.

190
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:26,000
After all, me being alive right now...

191
00:22:26,480 --> 00:22:28,200
is no different from being dead.

192
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,400
I don't lock my door when I sleep.

193
00:22:39,119 --> 00:22:41,239
There are plenty of knives
in the kitchen downstairs.

194
00:22:41,559 --> 00:22:43,079
Each one sharper than the last.

195
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,200
Or...

196
00:22:47,759 --> 00:22:48,759
you could use this.

197
00:22:50,279 --> 00:22:50,880
Take it.

198
00:22:51,039 --> 00:22:52,039
Take it.

199
00:22:53,839 --> 00:22:54,839
Just like this...

200
00:22:55,759 --> 00:22:56,759
plunge it in.

201
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:00,680
And you'll be free.

202
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:06,079
And I'll be free.

203
00:23:44,200 --> 00:23:45,200
Come in.

204
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:52,839
Mr. Lu.

205
00:23:53,039 --> 00:23:54,759
Should I arrange for someone for you today?

206
00:23:59,000 --> 00:24:00,000
That won't be necessary.

207
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:03,279
Was the person I picked
before not good enough?

208
00:24:07,799 --> 00:24:08,799
Xiao Cheng.

209
00:24:10,119 --> 00:24:11,640
Have a few drinks with me later.

210
00:24:13,559 --> 00:24:14,079
Okay.

211
00:24:14,559 --> 00:24:15,919
I'll wait for you downstairs then.

212
00:24:37,880 --> 00:24:38,599
Yichen. Yichen.

213
00:24:38,599 --> 00:24:39,160
Hey, you, come here.

214
00:24:39,161 --> 00:24:40,319
Give me a hand. Help me out.

215
00:24:41,000 --> 00:24:42,000
Sorry to bother you.

216
00:24:43,119 --> 00:24:43,759
He's had too much to drink.

217
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:45,200
Mr. Lu's room is upstairs.

218
00:24:46,079 --> 00:24:47,559
Well, I'll be going now.

219
00:24:47,839 --> 00:24:48,880
I'll leave Mr. Lu to you.

220
00:24:49,039 --> 00:24:50,039
He's all yours.

221
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:53,960
Xiao Chen.

222
00:25:03,640 --> 00:25:04,680
Xiao Chen.

223
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,160
Get off me.

224
00:25:51,359 --> 00:25:53,079
What's with the reluctance?

225
00:25:53,559 --> 00:25:55,239
It's not like we haven't done this before.

226
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,559
How could you be so cruel?

227
00:26:17,480 --> 00:26:18,599
Cheng Yichen.

228
00:26:33,079 --> 00:26:34,079
Maybe...

229
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,240
after we sleep together,

230
00:26:36,640 --> 00:26:38,680
if I think your performance isn't too bad,

231
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:40,319
I might just let you go.

232
00:26:56,119 --> 00:26:57,240
What do you want from me?

233
00:26:58,559 --> 00:26:59,559
I'm willing to touch you.

234
00:26:59,839 --> 00:27:01,319
You should be happy about that.

235
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,680
Why don't you consider this?

236
00:27:05,960 --> 00:27:07,960
Maybe I'm falling in love
with you all over again.

237
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:17,880
Don't do this.

238
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:19,279
I'm begging you.

239
00:27:20,039 --> 00:27:21,039
Lu Feng.

240
00:27:24,599 --> 00:27:25,599
Lu Feng.

241
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,799
Why did you kiss me?

242
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:01,880
Cheng Yichen.

243
00:28:02,599 --> 00:28:03,639
Let me tell you something.

244
00:28:04,400 --> 00:28:05,400
All these years,

245
00:28:05,559 --> 00:28:07,799
while you were off having
fun with someone else,

246
00:28:08,519 --> 00:28:09,599
there was someone...

247
00:28:11,240 --> 00:28:12,320
who was waiting for you.

248
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:13,960
And...

249
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:16,240
they were living like a dead man.

250
00:28:17,279 --> 00:28:18,319
Just think about it.

251
00:28:20,480 --> 00:28:21,480
How...

252
00:28:21,960 --> 00:28:23,280
ridiculous my life has been...

253
00:28:24,519 --> 00:28:25,920
all these years.

254
00:28:44,759 --> 00:28:45,759
Xiao Chen.

255
00:28:48,759 --> 00:28:49,759
Lu Feng.

256
00:28:52,240 --> 00:28:53,240
Xiao Chen.

257
00:28:53,880 --> 00:28:55,519
Just a few deep kisses.

258
00:28:56,039 --> 00:28:58,000
Just him whispering my name a few times.

259
00:28:59,319 --> 00:29:02,000
And the walls I'd built
up suddenly crumbled.

260
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:05,480
The cracks between us seemed
like a figment of my imagination.

261
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:09,160
It was as if the years of
pain had never piled up.

262
00:29:09,880 --> 00:29:12,000
As if he had never hurt me.

263
00:29:12,519 --> 00:29:14,480
As if I could be like I was before,

264
00:29:14,839 --> 00:29:17,359
giving myself to him without reservation.

265
00:29:19,599 --> 00:29:21,400
I guess longing and forgiveness...

266
00:29:22,599 --> 00:29:24,920
are never decided by logic.

267
00:29:33,400 --> 00:29:34,400
Lu Feng.

268
00:29:36,559 --> 00:29:38,559
I've really missed you so much.

269
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:58,680
Get out.

270
00:29:58,920 --> 00:30:00,119
So all the caresses,

271
00:30:01,240 --> 00:30:02,480
all the kisses,

272
00:30:04,039 --> 00:30:05,359
they were all fake.

273
00:30:06,559 --> 00:30:08,599
It was all in my head.

274
00:30:10,279 --> 00:30:13,680
He just wanted to make me suffer.

275
00:30:24,559 --> 00:30:25,559
Mr. Lu.

276
00:30:29,440 --> 00:30:30,440
Mr. Lu.

277
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:33,160
Should I arrange for someone today?

278
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,640
Yes, arrange it.

279
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:40,839
Get me the best-looking one you can find.

280
00:30:43,079 --> 00:30:44,079
Yes, sir.

281
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,160
Wait.

282
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:53,839
On second thought, forget it.

283
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:54,960
Understood, Mr. Lu.

284
00:31:27,839 --> 00:31:30,799
Mr. Lu, someone from the
Zhuo family came to the office.

285
00:31:31,079 --> 00:31:33,879
They said they have business they
want to discuss with you personally.

286
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,000
Business?

287
00:31:36,839 --> 00:31:37,999
Those were their exact words.

288
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:41,359
You tell them...

289
00:31:41,519 --> 00:31:42,558
that FC Corporation...

290
00:31:42,559 --> 00:31:45,039
will never have any business
dealings with the Zhuo family.

291
00:31:47,119 --> 00:31:48,119
Yes, sir.

292
00:34:12,559 --> 00:34:13,840
You should stay here for now.

293
00:34:14,480 --> 00:34:16,159
It's better for both you and Mr. Lu.

294
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:38,440
- Hello, Mr. Lu.
- Where is he?

295
00:35:38,719 --> 00:35:40,239
He's inside. Hasn't come out.

296
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:17,119
Cheng Yichen.

297
00:36:17,120 --> 00:36:18,240
What the hell are you doing?

298
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,840
Are you trying to get yourself killed?

299
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,360
Taking a bath.

300
00:36:22,559 --> 00:36:23,960
How long have you been in there?

301
00:36:40,719 --> 00:36:41,920
Are you trying to die?

302
00:36:43,199 --> 00:36:44,280
If you want to die,

303
00:36:45,039 --> 00:36:46,880
don't do it in my bathtub.

304
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:01,119
Are you afraid of what I might do to you?

305
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:12,800
Nothing's going to happen.

306
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,199
You don't have to worry at all.

307
00:39:25,039 --> 00:39:26,039
Brother Chen.

308
00:39:28,039 --> 00:39:29,719
Brother, it's really you!

309
00:39:31,559 --> 00:39:32,559
What are you doing here?

310
00:39:35,079 --> 00:39:36,599
What happened to your neck?

311
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:40,039
I just hurt it by accident.

312
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:42,440
Hurt it?

313
00:39:44,199 --> 00:39:45,559
It'll be fine in a couple of days.

314
00:39:45,679 --> 00:39:46,199
By the way,

315
00:39:46,599 --> 00:39:47,360
what are you doing here?

316
00:39:47,599 --> 00:39:48,599
This is my uncle's place.

317
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:51,199
You know, Mr. Lu.

318
00:39:51,639 --> 00:39:53,760
He said he'd take me to play tennis today.

319
00:39:54,599 --> 00:39:56,439
I have a school tournament next week,

320
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:57,440
so I need the practice.

321
00:39:57,719 --> 00:39:59,360
Brother, why don't you come with us?

322
00:40:00,159 --> 00:40:01,840
I... I don't know how to play.

323
00:40:02,039 --> 00:40:03,960
That's okay, you can learn.

324
00:40:04,079 --> 00:40:06,400
Mr. Lu isn't just a good player,

325
00:40:06,679 --> 00:40:07,799
he's an even better teacher.

326
00:40:08,239 --> 00:40:10,920
And he never gets mad.

327
00:40:12,159 --> 00:40:14,400
Even with someone as unathletic as me,

328
00:40:14,679 --> 00:40:16,119
he's never discouraging.

329
00:40:17,920 --> 00:40:19,120
Lu Feng is really good to you.

330
00:40:19,519 --> 00:40:20,519
Of course.

331
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:23,199
That's mainly because he's a great person.

332
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:25,320
By the way, Brother,

333
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:26,599
you still haven't told me...

334
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:28,119
why you're here today.

335
00:40:31,239 --> 00:40:32,719
Did you start working at his company?

336
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:34,960
How's it going?

337
00:40:36,639 --> 00:40:37,679
I...

338
00:40:39,079 --> 00:40:40,079
Ke Lo.

339
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,440
I got you a new racket.

340
00:40:43,199 --> 00:40:44,559
A new racket?

341
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:46,200
It's custom-made from overseas.

342
00:40:48,119 --> 00:40:50,760
That outfit really suits you.

343
00:40:52,639 --> 00:40:53,639
Mr. Lu.

344
00:40:54,800 --> 00:40:57,159
Should we take Brother
Chen to play with us?

345
00:40:58,239 --> 00:40:59,920
No, thanks. I don't know how.

346
00:41:01,119 --> 00:41:02,119
Don't worry about him.

347
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:04,199
But... him...

348
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:05,760
The car is here.

349
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:06,880
Let's go.

350
00:41:07,719 --> 00:41:08,719
But... but...

